asciidoc.html: The Eclipse Adoptium® project certifies that all Eclipse Temurin binaries available from adoptium.net except for those clearly marked as "intermediate builds" have passed all requirements of the then-current Java SE compatibility test suite (JCK tests), and are compliant and compatible implementations.
